stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> FREE: reset

    FREE --> PENDING: insert from CAM<br/>captures rank, bank, row,<br/>is_write, cam_slot_idx,<br/>row_hit_cached, age=0

    PENDING --> ISSUED: scheduler picks<br/>pick_one_hot[i]

    ISSUED --> COMPLETING: rd — first beat returns<br/>wr — last W beat issued

    COMPLETING --> FREE: rd — beats_returned == len<br/>wr — b_complete from xbank<br/>cleared by CAM strobe

    note right of PENDING
      Visible to scheduler every cycle.
      Each cycle: age++ (saturating).
      row_hit_cached refreshes on
      bank-state change (1-cycle lag).
    end note

    note right of ISSUED
      Hidden from scheduler
      (pick_valid_mask excludes
      ISSUED + COMPLETING).
      Slot still occupies queue cell.
    end note
